<header>
  <h1>AI-Powered Health Services</h1>
</header>

<main class="container">
  <div class="feature" id="chatbot-feature">
      <img src="https://img.icons8.com/fluency/48/chatbot.png" alt="Chatbot Icon">
      <h3>AI-Powered Chatbots</h3>
      <p>Get instant assistance for basic symptom checks and queries using our AI-driven chatbot technology.</p>
      <button id="chatbot-button">Start Chat</button>
      <input type="text" id="chatbot-input" placeholder="Type your symptoms here" style="margin-top: 1rem; display: block; width: 100%; padding: 0.5rem;" >
      <p id="chatbot-response" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-weight: bold;"></p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature" id="analytics-feature">
      <img src="https://img.icons8.com/fluency/48/combo-chart.png" alt="Analytics Icon">
      <h3>Real-Time Analytics</h3>
      <p>Monitor health trends and assess risks in real-time with advanced analytics tools.</p>
      <canvas id="analytics-chart"></canvas>
      <button id="chart-update-button" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Update Chart</button>
      <div id="chart-input">
          <label for="new-data">Enter new data values (comma-separated):</label>
          <input type="text" id="new-data" style="width: 100%; padding: 0.5rem;">
          <button id="add-data-button" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Add Data</button>
      </div>
  </div>

  <div class="feature" id="notifications-feature">
      <img src="https://img.icons8.com/fluency/48/appointment-reminders.png" alt="Notifications Icon">
      <h3>Notifications and Alerts</h3>
      <p>Stay updated with timely notifications and alerts about health updates and emergencies.</p>
      <button id="notifications-button">Show Notification</button>
      <p id="notification-response" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-weight: bold; color: red;"></p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature" id="delivery-feature">
      <img src="https://img.icons8.com/fluency/48/delivery.png" alt="Delivery Icon">
      <h3>Supply Delivery Requests</h3>
      <p>Easily request deliveries for food, medicine, and hygiene kits directly from our platform.</p>
      <button id="delivery-button">Request Supply</button>
      <p id="delivery-response" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-weight: bold; color: green;"></p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature" id="emergency-feature">
      <img src="https://tse1.mm.bing.net/th?id=OIP.SjiYIXNTjzRvNOs0qu8HwgHaHa&pid=Api&P=0&h=180" alt="Emergency Icon">
      <h3>Emergency Assistance</h3>
      <p>Get immediate help in case of emergencies with our 24/7 assistance feature.</p>
      <button id="emergency-button">Call for Help</button>
      <p id="emergency-response" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-weight: bold; color: blue;"></p>
  </div>
   <div class="feature" id="quarantine-feature">
      <img src="https://tse1.mm.bing.net/th?id=OIP.SU4qXcQFI34zaMcD2MUF7wHaH_&pid=Api&P=0&h=180" alt="Quarantine Icon">
      <h3>Quarantine Compliance</h3>
      <p>Track and ensure adherence to quarantine guidelines to keep everyone safe.</p>
      <button id="quarantine-button">Check Compliance</button>
      <p id="quarantine-response" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-weight: bold; color: orange;"></p>
  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  <p>&copy; 2025 AI Health Services. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>
